---
// Site-wide free-download band + footer with crisis line.
---

<!-- FREE DOWNLOAD / EMAIL CAPTURE BAND -->
<section class="capture">
  <div class="container capture-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Two short reads, free</p>
      <h2>Want a taste? Take whichever one fits where you are.</h2>
      <p class="capture-sub">
        A couple of pieces that do in a few minutes what the whole site is about: help something make sense.
      </p>
    </div>
    <form class="capture-form" name="download" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="download" />
      <p class="hidden-field"><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
      <label class="visually-hidden" for="cap-email">Email address</label>
      <input id="cap-email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send it to me</button>
      <p class="capture-fine">No spam. The download arrives by email, that's it.</p>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container foot-grid">
    <div class="foot-brand">
      <img src="/logo/logo-white.png" alt="Ennea Evolution" width="240" height="84" />
      <p class="foot-tag">Understanding. Then clarity. Then capability.</p>
      <p class="foot-contact">
        <a href="mailto:enneaevolution@gmail.com">enneaevolution@gmail.com</a><br />
        <a href="tel:+14358810193">435-881-0193</a><br />
        Cache Valley, Utah · and by Zoom
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="foot-col">
      <h4>Personal Work</h4>
      <a href="/personal-work">Overview</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/anxiety-overthinking">Anxiety & Overthinking</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/stay-or-go">Stay or Go</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/coming-back-to-yourself">Coming Back to Yourself</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/confidence-self-worth">Confidence & Self-Worth</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/the-distance-between-you">The Distance Between You</a>
      <a href="/personal-work/am-i-the-problem">Am I the Problem?</a>
    </div>

    <div class="foot-col">
      <h4>Professional Work</h4>
      <a href="/professional-work">Overview</a>
      <a href="/professional-work/people-make-sense">The People Make Sense Program</a>
      <a href="/professional-work/manage-with-meaning">Manage With Meaning</a>
      <a href="/professional-work/workshops">Workshops</a>
      <a href="/professional-work/employee-counseling-team-repair">Employee Counseling & Team Repair</a>
    </div>

    <div class="foot-col">
      <h4>More</h4>
      <a href="/about">About Candace</a>
      <a href="/get-started">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="crisis">
      If you are in crisis, please call or text <strong>988</strong> (Suicide &amp; Crisis Lifeline) or call
      <strong>911</strong>. This work is steady, preventative support and coaching. It is not crisis care.
    </div>
    <div class="legal">
      <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Ennea Evolution. Life evolves and so can we.</span>
      <span>Counseling &amp; coaching, not licensed therapy.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  /* capture band */
  .capture { background: var(--cream-2); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .capture-inner {
    padding-block: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.25rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .capture h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.6vw, 2.1rem); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .capture-sub { color: var(--body); margin: 0; max-width: 42ch; }
  .capture-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .capture-form input[type="email"] {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line-strong);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--paper);
    font: inherit;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .capture-form input[type="email"]:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--teal-tint); }
  .capture-form .btn { justify-content: center; }
  .capture-fine { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0.15rem 0 0; }
  .hidden-field { display: none; }
  .visually-hidden { position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0 0 0 0); }

  /* footer */
  .site-footer { background: var(--teal-950); color: #cfe0e2; padding-block: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem) 2rem; }
  .foot-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr 1.1fr 0.8fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .foot-brand img { height: 56px; width: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .foot-tag { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.15rem; color: #fff; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; }
  .foot-contact { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.9; color: #aecace; margin: 0; }
  .foot-contact a { color: #aecace; }
  .foot-contact a:hover { color: var(--marigold); }

  .foot-col h4 { color: var(--marigold); font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .foot-col a { display: block; color: #bdd3d5; font-size: 0.92rem; padding: 0.32rem 0; }
  .foot-col a:hover { color: #fff; }

  .crisis {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    padding-top: 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #9fbabd;
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
  .crisis strong { color: var(--marigold); }
  .legal {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #7fa0a3;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .capture-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .foot-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
